Package: openmediavault-themekit
Architecture: all
Depends: openmediavault (>= 8.1.1), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Custom theme, accent color and wallpaper plugin for openmediavault
 Adds a "Theme Kit" page under System that lets you pick light or dark
 mode, an accent color, and custom wallpapers for the login, standby
 and shutdown screens. Settings persist across openmediavault updates
 via an apt hook.
